properties.Name: InsurancePolicyRelationshipType
properties.Description:
A classification or categorization of relationships that may exist between Insurance Policies.

Ex:
- Umbrella Policy covers amounts exceeding limits on related policy
- Life insurance/other Insurer
- Additional policy/same Insurer
- Replacement Policy
- Exchange of like kind of policy
- Exchange of unlike kind of policy
- Policy belonging to a Group Policy
